headline: Market Chatter: Airbnb Expands Sublet-Friendly Rentals Program to London, UK Amid Criticism
summary: Airbnb (ABNB) launched its Airbnb-friendly apartments program in London effective Monday, allowing tenants in nearly 1,500 flats owned by Greystar to sublet their homes part-time, the Financial Times reported Monday.
